               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Malkǝʾa Māryām “Image of Mary” (fols. 3r-19v) (cp. Malkǝʾa gubaʾe,
                     ʾAśmära 1974 E.C., pp. 21-34.)
 II) Malkǝʾa ʾIyasus “Image of Jesus” (fols.
                     19v-34r) (the strophe "lä-ʾaḍabʿikä" is missing; cp. Malkǝʾa gubaʾe, ʾAśmära
                     1974 E.C., p. 44), incomplete
 
 Additiones 1-2.</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <locus from="3r" to="19v">3r-19v</locus>
                     <title corresp="LIT1858Malkea" type="complete">Malkǝʾa Māryām “Image of
                        Mary”</title>
                     <note>(cp. Malkǝʾa gubaʾe, ʾAśmära 1974 E.C., pp. 21-34.)</note>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                     <locus from="19v" to="34r">19v-34r</locus>
                     <title corresp="LIT2741RepCh25" type="incomplete">Malkǝʾa ʾIyasus “Image of
                        Jesus”</title>
                     <note>(the strophe "la-ʾaḍābʿika" is missing; cp. Malkǝʾa gubaʾe, ʾAśmära 1974
                        E.C., p. 44)</note>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
